quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  22,39,jin musalmanoon se ( khuwa makhuwa ) larai ki jati hai un ko ijazat hai ( ke woh bhi lrhin ) kyunkay un par zulm ho raha hai. aur khuda ( un ki madad kere ga woh ) yaqeenan un ki madad par Qadir hai
  22,40,yeh woh log hain ke apne gharon se na-haq nikaal diye gay ( unhon ne kuch qasoor nahikiya ) haan yeh kehte hain ke hamara perwar-digaar khuda hai. aur agar khuda logon ko aik dosray se nah htata rehta to ( rahibon ke ) sawamay aur ( esaion ke ) girgay aur ( yahudion ke ) ibadat khanaay aur ( musalmanoon ki ) msjdin jin mein khuda ka bohat sa zikarkiya jata hai weraan hochuki hoten. aur jo shakhs khuda ki madad karta hai khuda is ki zaroor madad karta hai. be shak khuda tawana aur ghalib hai
  22,41,yeh woh log hain ke agar hum un ko malik mein dustarus den to namaz parheen aur zakaat ada karen aur naik kaam karne ka hukum den aur buray kamon se mana karen aur sab kamon ka injaam khuda hi ke ikhtiyar mein hai
  22,42,aur agar yeh log tum ko jutlatay hain un se pehlay Nooh ki qoum aur Aad وﺛمود bhi ( apne payghambaroon ko ) jhutla chuke hain
  22,43,aur qoum ibrahim aur qoum Loot bhi
  22,44,aur Mudin ke rehne walay bhi. aur moose bhi to ghutlaye ja chukay hain lekin mein kafiroon ko mohlat deta raha phir un ko pakar liya. to ( dekh lau ) ke mera azaab kaisa ( sakht ) tha
  22,45,aur bohat si bastiyan hain ke hum ne un ko tabah kar dala ke woh nafarman theen. so woh apni chaton par giri pari hain. aur ( bohat se ) kunwein be car aur ( bohat se ) mehal weraan parre hain
  22,46,kiya un logon ne malik mein sair nahi ki taakay un ke dil ( aisay ) hotay ke un se samajh satke. aur kaan ( aisay ) hotay ke un se sun satke. baat yeh hai ke ankhen andhi nahi hoten balkay dil jo seenon mein hain ( woh ) andhay hotay hain
